Google Adsense

ads on google search
Advertiser: Nike: shoes, running, sport shoes

"running shoes"

1. signup for google adsense
2. put JS tag on any page where you want to show the ads.
3. when a user loads the page, this JS tag will get executed by the browser
4. JS will send request to Adsense
5. URL for the page --> get content of the url.
6. analyze the html and extract important keywords


